Comment: 0,0:00:25.79,0:00:27.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Every day, the sky flows on,{\i0}
Comment: 0,0:00:27.71,0:00:30.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}as if a "play" button\Nhas been pressed again and again.{\i0}
Comment: 0,0:00:32.01,0:00:33.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}A scene that never changes.{\i0}
Comment: 0,0:00:34.18,0:00:35.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}No dissatisfaction.{\i0}
Comment: 0,0:00:35.89,0:00:38.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}That must be proof of peace.{\i0}
Comment: 0,0:00:38.93,0:00:43.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}I was scouted out and entered show business,\Nbut the world didn't change otherwise for me.{\i0}
Comment: 0,0:00:44.56,0:00:49.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Shooting is starting today for the drama\Nthat will mark my debut as an actor.{\i0}
Comment: 0,0:00:49.77,0:00:52.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}As always,\Neverything was pretty much going smoothly.{\i0}
Comment: 0,0:00:53.86,0:00:56.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I'm Taguchi, Junta Azumaya's manager.
Comment: 0,0:00:56.78,0:00:59.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Azumaya, this is the director, Mr. Kadokura.
Comment: 0,0:00:59.66,0:01:01.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I'm Junta Azumaya.
Comment: 0,0:01:01.91,0:01:03.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Nice to meet you.
Comment: 0,0:01:03.87,0:01:05.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,N-Nice to meet you!
Comment: 0,0:01:05.58,0:01:06.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}He's hooked!{\i0}
Comment: 0,0:01:06.58,0:01:08.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Y-You're really popular right now, huh?
Comment: 0,0:01:08.83,0:01:11.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Your hair and eye color are light.\NMaybe you're half-Japanese?
Comment: 0,0:01:11.38,0:01:13.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,My grandfather is a Spaniard...
Comment: 0,0:01:12.38,0:01:14.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}Mr. Saijo! Good morning!
Comment: 0,0:01:14.55,0:01:16.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Good morning!
Comment: 0,0:01:16.22,0:01:17.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Good morning.
Comment: 0,0:01:17.76,0:01:19.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,There's Takato!
Comment: 0,0:01:19.09,0:01:20.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Hi, Saijo!
Comment: 0,0:01:20.68,0:01:21.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Long time no see.
Comment: 0,0:01:26.14,0:01:27.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}So this person is...{\i0}
Comment: 0,0:01:28.90,0:01:30.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Takato Saijo.{\i0}
Comment: 0,0:03:04.28,0:03:08.75,Title,NTP,0,0,0,,hug 7 "Can I keep liking you?"
Comment: 0,0:03:05.33,0:03:09.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}It's a pleasure to meet you.\NI'm Junta Azumaya from Mitsuya Production.
Comment: 0,0:03:09.46,0:03:10.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}I look forward to working with you.
Comment: 0,0:03:15.54,0:03:19.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Oh. I'm glad to have the chance\Nto work with you on your drama debut.
Comment: 0,0:03:19.97,0:03:21.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Let's make this a great one.
Comment: 0,0:03:21.68,0:03:22.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Yes!
Comment: 0,0:03:23.97,0:03:26.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Was he appraising me?{\i0}
Comment: 0,0:03:27.47,0:03:31.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}"Vial of the Sun" was a pure love story\Nabout a young perfumer with an eye disease{\i0}
Comment: 0,0:03:31.77,0:03:35.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}and a girl who aims to become a glass artisan.{\i0}
Comment: 0,0:03:36.02,0:03:40.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}My role was an aspiring potter and old friend\Nof the heroine who's in love with her.{\i0}
Comment: 0,0:03:41.45,0:03:43.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Cut! Okay, we got it!
Comment: 0,0:03:43.53,0:03:45.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Then next,\Nthe scene between Hinata and Satomi.
Comment: 0,0:03:45.99,0:03:46.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Okay!
Comment: 0,0:03:47.58,0:03:49.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Azumaya, is this really your first time?
Comment: 0,0:03:49.79,0:03:51.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,That was great!
Comment: 0,0:03:51.33,0:03:52.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Comment: 0,0:03:53.42,0:03:55.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}So I guess how I did that was good.{\i0}
Comment: 0,0:03:55.75,0:03:59.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}For now, it looks like\Ndoing the usual would suffice.{\i0}
Comment: 0,0:04:07.51,0:04:08.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Um...{\i0}
Comment: 0,0:04:09.64,0:04:11.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}what is this?{\i0}
Comment: 0,0:04:12.27,0:04:13.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Whoa, whoa, whoa, whoa!
Comment: 0,0:04:14.14,0:04:15.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Stop! Stop!
Comment: 0,0:04:15.94,0:04:18.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,What's with this girl's performance?
Comment: 0,0:04:16.86,0:04:19.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}Ugh, there he is. Sakamaki, the producer!
Comment: 0,0:04:19.36,0:04:24.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I'm sure this is a tough job for a cheesecake\Nmodel, but you've still gotta do your best!
Comment: 0,0:04:19.82,0:04:22.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}Don't get too close to him, otherwise you'll\Nfeel like you want to punch him.
Comment: 0,0:04:24.11,0:04:27.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}Wow, he looks like pink fish floss.{\i0}
Comment: 0,0:04:26.70,0:04:29.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,M-Mr. Sakamaki!\NHer performance wasn't that bad.
Comment: 0,0:04:29.08,0:04:31.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,All right, fine, I guess I've got to lecture you
Comment: 0,0:04:31.41,0:04:33.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,on the creative frame of mind\Nthat's needed for a drama.
Comment: 0,0:04:33.87,0:04:36.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I'll take you out drinking afterwards, okay?
Comment: 0,0:04:36.50,0:04:38.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,First workplace harassment,\Nthen sexual harassment.
Comment: 0,0:04:39.00,0:04:43.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}I wonder if rescuing her here\Nwould have an effect on my next job.{\i0}
Comment: 0,0:04:41.09,0:04:42.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Comment: 0,0:04:43.92,0:04:46.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Are you off tomorrow? You're off, right?
Comment: 0,0:04:44.38,0:04:46.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}Oh, what the hell.{\i0}
Comment: 0,0:04:46.68,0:04:48.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}Hey, Azumaya?!
Comment: 0,0:04:46.68,0:04:49.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Yeah. Then what should we do?
Comment: 0,0:04:49.05,0:04:50.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I guess go to Ginza? Get some sushi...
Comment: 0,0:04:54.85,0:04:56.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Comment: 0,0:04:56.31,0:05:00.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,If we're not going to continue here,\Ncan we go on to my next scene?
Comment: 0,0:05:01.82,0:05:03.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,We're just wasting time.
Comment: 0,0:05:05.07,0:05:07.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,This has such a gentle form.
Comment: 0,0:05:07.36,0:05:11.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,It doesn't have the stiffness of glass\Nand as I'm holding it, it feels warm.
Comment: 0,0:05:14.50,0:05:15.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,What?
Comment: 0,0:05:15.92,0:05:16.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I knew it.
Comment: 0,0:05:17.04,0:05:18.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,You're the same as this vial.
Comment: 0,0:05:19.04,0:05:21.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,The scent of the warm sun.
Comment: 0,0:05:21.84,0:05:23.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Did you make this?
Comment: 0,0:05:24.51,0:05:27.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}He delivers such an elegant performance.{\i0}
Comment: 0,0:05:27.30,0:05:29.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's like every moment is thoughtful.{\i0}
Comment: 0,0:05:29.97,0:05:31.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}My eyes want to follow him\Nall the way to his fingertips.{\i0}
Comment: 0,0:05:32.77,0:05:35.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}I like this pure feeling of tension.{\i0}
Comment: 0,0:05:35.89,0:05:39.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}It feels like he brings an air of dignity\Nto this whole set.{\i0}
Comment: 0,0:05:39.94,0:05:41.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Cut! Okay, we got it!
Comment: 0,0:05:42.19,0:05:44.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Well, I'll be on my way.
Comment: 0,0:05:44.61,0:05:46.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,S-See you tomorrow!
Comment: 0,0:05:46.74,0:05:48.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Th-That's my Saijo!
Comment: 0,0:05:48.82,0:05:51.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,You're in a whole other league\Nthan those newbies! Good, good!
Comment: 0,0:05:51.66,0:05:52.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,You.
Comment: 0,0:05:52.91,0:05:54.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,You're in my way.
Comment: 0,0:05:55.41,0:05:57.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,S-Sorry.
Comment: 0,0:05:57.71,0:05:58.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Comment: 0,0:06:02.29,0:06:05.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}Saijo was in a bad mood\Nbecause you were doing a terrible job!
Comment: 0,0:06:05.76,0:06:07.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}You better apologize to him later!
Comment: 0,0:06:08.38,0:06:10.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,It's almost impressive how small-time he is.
Comment: 0,0:06:10.80,0:06:12.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}The pink fish floss logged out?{\i0}
Comment: 0,0:06:13.26,0:06:17.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Um, I apologize for making Mr. Saijo angry.
Comment: 0,0:06:17.43,0:06:23.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Oh, no, I think Saijo just put on\Na good act to divert Mr. Sakamaki.
Comment: 0,0:06:23.94,0:06:27.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}By doing that, Mr. Sakamaki\Nhad to start worrying about Saijo's mood
Comment: 0,0:06:27.65,0:06:30.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}and wasn't able\Nto pick a quarrel with any of us.
Comment: 0,0:06:30.16,0:06:32.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}To be honest, that was really my job.
Comment: 0,0:06:32.99,0:06:33.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}I'm pathetic.
Comment: 0,0:06:34.83,0:06:37.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Takato, you have to be so cool.
Comment: 0,0:06:41.21,0:06:43.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}So this is what it's like\Nto be on the set of a drama.{\i0}
Comment: 0,0:06:44.50,0:06:47.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}I don't think it's like anything\NI've experienced before. Especially...{\i0}
Comment: 0,0:06:47.59,0:06:49.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I'd like to order catering for the set,
Comment: 0,0:06:49.80,0:06:52.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,and please add an assortment of sweets\Nthat girls would like.
Comment: 0,0:06:53.55,0:06:56.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Yeah, I just want to improve\Nmorale on the set a bit.
Comment: 0,0:06:57.22,0:06:59.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Mr. Saijo didn't go home?{\i0}
Comment: 0,0:07:00.02,0:07:03.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I'm fine. How many years\Ndo you think I've been doing this?
Comment: 0,0:07:04.61,0:07:09.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}Strong people like him are just\Npicture-perfect just by doing that.{\i0}
Comment: 0,0:07:05.19,0:07:07.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Yeah, sorry for the hassle, Mr. Sasaki.
Comment: 0,0:07:07.53,0:07:09.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Please put the order in. Thanks.
Comment: 0,0:07:12.36,0:07:17.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,The next time that producer\Nrears his head and shows up on set,
Comment: 0,0:07:17.37,0:07:21.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I'll embarrass him so badly\Nthat he'll never wear pink again.
Comment: 0,0:07:24.75,0:07:26.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"Creative frame of mind," whatever!
Comment: 0,0:07:26.84,0:07:29.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,You oughta recreate yourself\Nfrom before you were born!
Comment: 0,0:07:30.63,0:07:33.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}I see. This is what he's like.{\i0}
Comment: 0,0:07:34.80,0:07:36.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}His face that's not on set...{\i0}
Comment: 0,0:07:36.76,0:07:40.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}I mean, it's really different,\Nbut oh man, it's hilarious!{\i0}
Comment: 0,0:07:37.14,0:07:40.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}I need more sugar! Come on,\Nserotonin! Give me some more!
Comment: 0,0:07:41.77,0:07:46.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Well, enough of that little fish,\Nbut this Junta Azumaya...
Comment: 0,0:07:48.36,0:07:51.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,It's been a while since I've had to contend\Nwith a major annoyance.
Comment: 0,0:07:52.86,0:07:53.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}I see.{\i0}
Comment: 0,0:07:55.20,0:07:58.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}He's always been looking at me with hostility.{\i0}
Comment: 0,0:07:59.50,0:08:02.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}I guess this is what it feels like to be hated.{\i0}
Comment: 0,0:08:04.63,0:08:05.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Mr. Saijo.
Comment: 0,0:08:06.21,0:08:07.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Good work today.
Comment: 0,0:08:07.88,0:08:09.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,A-Azumaya?!
Comment: 0,0:08:09.05,0:08:10.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,You like hot chocolate?
Comment: 0,0:08:13.59,0:08:15.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,How long have you been here, Azumaya?
Comment: 0,0:08:15.64,0:08:16.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Not long.
Comment: 0,0:08:16.47,0:08:17.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Oh, I see.
Comment: 0,0:08:17.64,0:08:19.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,By "not long,"\Nyou mean like four or five minutes?
Comment: 0,0:08:19.47,0:08:21.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,No, about 30 seconds.
Comment: 0,0:08:21.48,0:08:22.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Oh, really?
Comment: 0,0:08:23.98,0:08:26.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Mr. Saijo, thank you for earlier.
Comment: 0,0:08:28.07,0:08:30.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Oh, you knew what I was doing, huh?
Comment: 0,0:08:30.48,0:08:32.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Mr. Kadokura explained it.
Comment: 0,0:08:32.86,0:08:33.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Oh.
Comment: 0,0:08:34.03,0:08:35.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I owe him one.
Comment: 0,0:08:36.70,0:08:41.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}His eyelashes are so long\Nthat they cast a shadow.{\i0}
Comment: 0,0:08:37.16,0:08:39.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}Then I don't have to spell it out.
Comment: 0,0:08:41.45,0:08:45.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Well, if things have quieted down over there,\NI'll return to the studio.
Comment: 0,0:08:45.71,0:08:47.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I have to thank Mr. Kadokura.
Comment: 0,0:08:47.92,0:08:49.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Um, Mr. Saijo...
Comment: 0,0:08:50.21,0:08:55.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I really am grateful\Nto have this chance to work with you.
Comment: 0,0:08:55.51,0:08:57.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I look forward to working with you\Nuntil this wraps.
Comment: 0,0:08:59.05,0:09:00.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,You're grateful?
Comment: 0,0:09:01.06,0:09:03.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Then I'd better work hard, too.
Comment: 0,0:09:03.81,0:09:07.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,So you'll continue to feel that way\Nto the very end.
Comment: 0,0:09:13.11,0:09:15.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Let's work well together, Azumaya.
Comment: 0,0:09:19.37,0:09:20.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Huh?{\i0}
Comment: 0,0:09:20.58,0:09:23.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}What is this?{\i0}
Comment: 0,0:09:24.12,0:09:25.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}My chest.{\i0}
Comment: 0,0:09:28.42,0:09:33.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}For the first time,\NI heard the sound of a noisy sky.{\i0}
Comment: 0,0:09:43.77,0:09:49.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}He slowly opens his eyes as if exhaling,\Nand then I know he'll look at me.{\i0}
Comment: 0,0:09:50.73,0:09:56.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}His expressions, and the way he moves his gaze.\NIt satisfies all the viewers with his performance.{\i0}
Comment: 0,0:09:56.82,0:09:58.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}He gives us what we want.{\i0}
Comment: 0,0:09:59.16,0:10:00.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}What we want?{\i0}
Comment: 0,0:10:01.20,0:10:02.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}What do I want?{\i0}
Comment: 0,0:10:03.29,0:10:05.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Where does that come from?{\i0}
Comment: 0,0:10:06.04,0:10:08.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}This stirring in the pit of my stomach...{\i0}
Comment: 0,0:10:09.71,0:10:12.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}What the hell is it?{\i0}
Comment: 0,0:10:13.59,0:10:16.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I like him. That's why I'm with him.
Comment: 0,0:10:16.34,0:10:20.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Eventually he won't be able\Nto see you or your work anymore.
Comment: 0,0:10:20.47,0:10:21.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Even if he can't see...
Comment: 0,0:10:21.80,0:10:25.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Even if he can't see, he'll know by touch.
Comment: 0,0:10:25.18,0:10:26.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,He'll sense me through scent.
Comment: 0,0:10:27.31,0:10:29.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Hinata, choose me.
Comment: 0,0:10:29.40,0:10:31.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Kosuke, let's stop talking about this.
Comment: 0,0:10:31.81,0:10:36.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Be mine. I'll always look at you,\Njust as I have all this time.
Comment: 0,0:10:36.69,0:10:38.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Wait, Kosuke!
Comment: 0,0:10:38.49,0:10:41.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Cut! Azumaya, Natsume, good work!
Comment: 0,0:10:42.24,0:10:43.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Good work!
Comment: 0,0:10:43.28,0:10:44.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Good work.
Comment: 0,0:10:54.92,0:10:55.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Pardon me.
Comment: 0,0:10:59.34,0:11:01.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Good work today.
Comment: 0,0:11:01.18,0:11:02.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Yeah, good work.
Comment: 0,0:11:02.97,0:11:07.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}What should I do? It's just the two of us,\Nbut it'll be awkward if I sit far away from him.{\i0}
Comment: 0,0:11:08.39,0:11:09.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Can I sit next to you?
Comment: 0,0:11:11.85,0:11:12.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Go ahead.
Comment: 0,0:11:12.90,0:11:15.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}He totally doesn't want me there.{\i0}
Comment: 0,0:11:20.82,0:11:24.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}This is awkward,\Nbut maybe I'll ask him about before.{\i0}
Comment: 0,0:11:24.70,0:11:27.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}If there's something I've done\Nto offend him, I'll apologize.{\i0}
Comment: 0,0:11:27.91,0:11:29.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Um, Mr. Saijo, I—
Comment: 0,0:11:29.75,0:11:30.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I like him.
Comment: 0,0:11:33.08,0:11:35.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I like him. That's why I'm with him.
Comment: 0,0:11:35.59,0:11:37.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- Um, Mr. Saijo?\N- Next line.
Comment: 0,0:11:38.42,0:11:39.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}From that last scene.{\i0}
Comment: 0,0:11:40.38,0:11:45.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Eventually he won't be able\Nto see you or your work anymore.
Comment: 0,0:11:45.60,0:11:47.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Even if he can't see...
Comment: 0,0:11:47.01,0:11:50.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Even if he can't see, he'll know by touch.
Comment: 0,0:11:50.35,0:11:52.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- He'll sense me through—\N- Choose me.
Comment: 0,0:11:52.23,0:11:54.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Kosuke, let's stop talking about—
Comment: 0,0:11:54.02,0:11:56.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Be mine. I'll...
Comment: 0,0:11:56.82,0:11:58.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hold her gently in my arms...{\i0}
Comment: 0,0:11:58.61,0:12:01.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}No, hold her as if I'm stealing her away.{\i0}
Comment: 0,0:12:01.90,0:12:06.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I'll always look at you,\Njust as I have all this time.
Comment: 0,0:12:07.03,0:12:08.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll follow my feelings.{\i0}
Comment: 0,0:12:08.79,0:12:10.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Azumaya.
Comment: 0,0:12:10.45,0:12:12.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,That was much better.
Comment: 0,0:12:12.83,0:12:15.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Much better than just saying the lines.
Comment: 0,0:12:15.50,0:12:19.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Instead of thinking it out logically,\Nyou're more suited to act from your emotions.
Comment: 0,0:12:20.17,0:12:22.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Maybe you should learn more about yourself.
Comment: 0,0:12:22.80,0:12:24.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,About myself?
Comment: 0,0:12:25.55,0:12:27.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I swear, you're sitting on a gold mine.
Comment: 0,0:12:27.89,0:12:31.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Um, Mr. Saijo. I wonder what it is that I want.
Comment: 0,0:12:32.23,0:12:33.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Nothing!
Comment: 0,0:12:33.69,0:12:35.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Comment: 0,0:12:36.81,0:12:39.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Well, I'm going to take a nap\Nuntil we get to the location.
Comment: 0,0:12:39.07,0:12:41.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Right! Good night.
Comment: 0,0:12:44.74,0:12:48.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}The me I didn't know about\Nis slowly being dragged out.{\i0}
Comment: 0,0:12:50.49,0:12:53.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}What is it about him?{\i0}
Comment: 0,0:12:56.42,0:12:57.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,And action!
Comment: 0,0:12:58.88,0:13:01.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Are you okay walking around at night?
Comment: 0,0:13:03.05,0:13:04.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,You're...
Comment: 0,0:13:04.13,0:13:06.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Don't you remember me?
Comment: 0,0:13:06.72,0:13:11.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Or maybe you can't see faces now\Nfrom this distance?
Comment: 0,0:13:11.89,0:13:15.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,You're Kosuke, right? I recognize your voice.
Comment: 0,0:13:15.06,0:13:16.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,You don't get it, do you?
Comment: 0,0:13:17.15,0:13:18.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,But I do.
Comment: 0,0:13:18.27,0:13:20.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I know that you treasure her.
Comment: 0,0:13:21.11,0:13:22.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I know what you want to tell me.
Comment: 0,0:13:23.28,0:13:24.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I understand perfectly.
Comment: 0,0:13:25.78,0:13:26.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Mr. Amamiya.
Comment: 0,0:13:26.95,0:13:30.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}The lines, the emotions,\Nare coming out of me naturally.{\i0}
Comment: 0,0:13:30.83,0:13:34.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}I want to throw everything I have at him.\NMore, more.{\i0}
Comment: 0,0:13:35.41,0:13:37.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Mr. Amamiya, regarding her, how do you—
Comment: 0,0:13:45.67,0:13:47.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}I told you to inspect that!
Comment: 0,0:13:47.22,0:13:49.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}- I-I'm sorry! Towels! Towels!\N- Are you okay, Mr. Saijo?
Comment: 0,0:13:54.60,0:13:55.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}I heard a sound.{\i0}
Comment: 0,0:13:58.65,0:13:59.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}Azumaya.
Comment: 0,0:13:59.69,0:14:03.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}In my mind, the sky is roiling.{\i0}
Comment: 0,0:14:00.52,0:14:03.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}Why did you...
Comment: 0,0:14:05.57,0:14:07.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Why are you cowering like that?{\i0}
Comment: 0,0:14:08.91,0:14:11.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Why do you look at me like that?{\i0}
Comment: 0,0:14:09.57,0:14:11.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}What?
Comment: 0,0:14:13.54,0:14:16.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Is it because you hate me?{\i0}
Comment: 0,0:14:14.04,0:14:16.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}Azu... maya...
Comment: 0,0:14:21.96,0:14:23.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Saijo! Azumaya!
Comment: 0,0:14:23.92,0:14:24.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Are you okay?
Comment: 0,0:14:25.21,0:14:26.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Yes.
Comment: 0,0:14:27.13,0:14:30.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I'm not that wet,\Nso please take care of Azumaya.
Comment: 0,0:14:30.59,0:14:31.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,O-Okay!
Comment: 0,0:14:32.10,0:14:34.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Sorry. But thanks.
Comment: 0,0:14:34.89,0:14:35.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Not at all.
Comment: 0,0:14:36.89,0:14:39.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}What was I doing?{\i0}
Comment: 0,0:14:41.31,0:14:42.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Okay.{\i0}
Comment: 0,0:14:42.90,0:14:45.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}I would give everything to you.{\i0}
Comment: 0,0:14:46.82,0:14:50.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}If we hadn't been interrupted,\NI would've kissed him.{\i0}
Comment: 0,0:14:51.41,0:14:52.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kiss?{\i0}
Comment: 0,0:14:52.45,0:14:55.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}No. It wouldn't have been\Nanything that gentle.{\i0}
Comment: 0,0:14:56.12,0:14:57.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}I've never felt that before.{\i0}
Comment: 0,0:14:58.33,0:15:00.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}It was as if I'd become a beast.{\i0}
Comment: 0,0:15:02.42,0:15:05.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}For just a moment, he looked scared.{\i0}
Comment: 0,0:15:06.42,0:15:08.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Maybe he hates me again?
Comment: 0,0:15:13.60,0:15:17.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}This must be what he saw.{\i0}
Comment: 0,0:15:17.68,0:15:20.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}The face of a man overcome with desire.{\i0}
Comment: 0,0:15:22.10,0:15:23.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I'm in love with you.
Comment: 0,0:15:23.15,0:15:24.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,W-Wait, Kosuke.
Comment: 0,0:15:24.48,0:15:25.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I can't wait.
Comment: 0,0:15:25.65,0:15:27.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I've waited long enough.
Comment: 0,0:15:29.86,0:15:30.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Hinata.
Comment: 0,0:15:31.41,0:15:32.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,That was great!
Comment: 0,0:15:32.78,0:15:35.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,That was the best of all your scenes together.
Comment: 0,0:15:35.28,0:15:38.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Azumaya, what the heck?\NA sudden awakening!
Comment: 0,0:15:38.58,0:15:39.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Awakening?
Comment: 0,0:15:39.66,0:15:41.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,You seem different ever since that last location.
Comment: 0,0:15:41.92,0:15:43.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Did something cause it?
Comment: 0,0:15:49.42,0:15:51.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Yes, there was something.
Comment: 0,0:15:58.68,0:15:59.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Huh?{\i0}
Comment: 0,0:16:01.10,0:16:03.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Mr. Saijo, are you not feeling well?
Comment: 0,0:16:04.86,0:16:06.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,You're looking a little pale.
Comment: 0,0:16:07.86,0:16:09.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,No, I'm fine.
Comment: 0,0:16:10.28,0:16:12.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I'm glad you have enough confidence\Nto worry about my well-being.
Comment: 0,0:16:13.66,0:16:15.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,But be sure you stay focused.
Comment: 0,0:16:16.66,0:16:17.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Right.
Comment: 0,0:16:18.74,0:16:21.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,But, um, I think you have a slight fever.
Comment: 0,0:16:30.01,0:16:31.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Comment: 0,0:16:31.05,0:16:33.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,No, it's my fault. I apologize.
Comment: 0,0:16:38.22,0:16:40.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}It hurts. It hurts, but...{\i0}
Comment: 0,0:16:41.18,0:16:45.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}that one moment of contact, even with\Nthat moment of pain, it follows through.{\i0}
Comment: 0,0:16:48.86,0:16:51.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Excuse me. I'm getting on.
Comment: 0,0:16:58.58,0:16:59.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,About before...
Comment: 0,0:16:59.91,0:17:02.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- Yes?\N- Did I hurt your hand?
Comment: 0,0:17:03.33,0:17:05.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,No, it was nothing.
Comment: 0,0:17:05.58,0:17:07.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Oh. Good.
Comment: 0,0:17:08.34,0:17:12.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,One actor hurting another\Nis no laughing matter.
Comment: 0,0:17:14.13,0:17:16.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}I want to hug his shoulders to hold him up.{\i0}
Comment: 0,0:17:16.59,0:17:17.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}But...{\i0}
Comment: 0,0:17:18.55,0:17:22.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}But I'm sure he just wants to hurry and get away\Nfrom me, and out of this enclosed space.{\i0}
Comment: 0,0:17:26.15,0:17:28.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Is he really okay?{\i0}
Comment: 0,0:17:28.77,0:17:31.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}He seems to be walking normally, but...{\i0}
Comment: 0,0:17:32.57,0:17:36.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Worrying about him too much\Nwill only put him in a fouler mood.{\i0}
Comment: 0,0:17:39.28,0:17:40.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Mr. Saijo!
Comment: 0,0:17:42.12,0:17:43.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Pardon me.
Comment: 0,0:17:44.54,0:17:47.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,You're a lot warmer than I thought.\NThe hospital...
Comment: 0,0:17:48.79,0:17:50.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Crap. I only have my motorcycle.
Comment: 0,0:17:51.71,0:17:53.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Excuse me. I need a taxi.
Comment: 0,0:17:53.59,0:17:56.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,The location is the studio in Aoumi.\NYes, that's right.
Comment: 0,0:17:57.30,0:17:59.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Yes. Thank you.
Comment: 0,0:18:01.64,0:18:05.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I know you don't want to be touched by me,\Nbut please endure it for now.
Comment: 0,0:18:12.44,0:18:17.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}So the desire to treasure someone is connected\Nto the desire of wanting someone all to yourself.{\i0}
Comment: 0,0:18:18.53,0:18:19.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Mr. Saijo.{\i0}
Comment: 0,0:18:20.57,0:18:22.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}I've fallen in love with you.{\i0}
Comment: 0,0:18:23.70,0:18:26.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm sorry. Even if you hate me...{\i0}
Comment: 0,0:18:27.96,0:18:30.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Can I keep liking you?
Comment: 0,0:18:35.80,0:18:39.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Oh, there it is.\NSasaki here. I'm coming in!
Comment: 0,0:18:39.80,0:18:40.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Good evening!
Comment: 0,0:18:40.93,0:18:42.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Good evening.
Comment: 0,0:18:42.05,0:18:43.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I apologize that you went to all this trouble.
Comment: 0,0:18:43.89,0:18:45.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,No, no trouble at all.
Comment: 0,0:18:45.56,0:18:48.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,The doctor said that with\Nthe IV and plenty of sleep, he should be fine.
Comment: 0,0:18:48.60,0:18:53.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I wondered what it was about\Nwhen you called my agency.
Comment: 0,0:18:53.11,0:18:55.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,It must've been tough getting him here,\Ncarrying a tall man like him.
Comment: 0,0:18:56.24,0:18:58.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,No, he was light.
Comment: 0,0:18:58.61,0:19:01.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I was a little surprised by how slender he is.
Comment: 0,0:19:01.95,0:19:04.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Oh, don't tell him that, okay?
Comment: 0,0:19:04.33,0:19:07.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,He has a complex about how hard it is\Nfor him to put on muscle.
Comment: 0,0:19:11.00,0:19:12.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,You can go, Azumaya.
Comment: 0,0:19:13.25,0:19:14.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Thank you for tonight.
Comment: 0,0:19:14.55,0:19:17.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,When Takato wakes up,\NI'll tell him everything you did.
Comment: 0,0:19:18.59,0:19:21.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,If possible, please don't tell him\NI carried him here.
Comment: 0,0:19:23.05,0:19:24.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Are you self-conscious about it?
Comment: 0,0:19:24.97,0:19:25.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Yes.
Comment: 0,0:19:26.27,0:19:30.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}It seems that I've done nothing\Nbut annoy Mr. Saijo this shoot.
Comment: 0,0:19:30.02,0:19:34.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}Don't let him get to you.\NHe's the one who gets cranky all the time.
Comment: 0,0:19:34.73,0:19:35.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}Oh, come on.
Comment: 0,0:19:36.19,0:19:39.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,It's unusual for him to so openly\Ntreat someone like an enemy.
Comment: 0,0:19:40.36,0:19:43.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Maybe that means\Nhe has great expectations for you.
Comment: 0,0:19:58.55,0:20:02.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}This pain, heartache, sweetness, and rush...{\i0}
Comment: 0,0:20:04.14,0:20:06.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}I probably can't make them vanish.{\i0}
Comment: 0,0:20:09.27,0:20:10.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}A motorcycle is no good.{\i0}
Comment: 0,0:20:10.77,0:20:12.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}I need to get a car.{\i0}
Comment: 0,0:20:12.69,0:20:16.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}So I can give a ride to the person dear to me\Nwhenever they might need one.{\i0}
Comment: 0,0:20:18.19,0:20:21.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}This shoot is almost over.{\i0}
Comment: 0,0:20:24.57,0:20:27.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Okay, please stay like this\Nuntil they call for you.
Comment: 0,0:20:27.70,0:20:29.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Roger that.
Comment: 0,0:20:32.46,0:20:35.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}This is the last day.{\i0}
Comment: 0,0:20:40.92,0:20:43.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}No. I won't let it be the last day.{\i0}
Comment: 0,0:20:45.39,0:20:49.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Since meeting you, I've learned\Nwhat it is to truly "want" something.{\i0}
Comment: 0,0:20:50.60,0:20:53.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm going to chase you, Takato.{\i0}
Comment: 0,0:20:59.53,0:21:02.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}So that the next time we meet,\Nwe'll be side by side{\i0}
Comment: 0,0:21:02.74,0:21:07.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}and I'll be able to express these feelings\Nand take you in my arms.{\i0}
Comment: 0,0:21:07.91,0:21:12.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll firm my resolve, and start preparing myself\Nso I can obtain what's precious to me.{\i0}
Comment: 0,0:21:18.34,0:21:21.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,First off, could we have a few words\Nfrom our lead actor, Azumaya?
Comment: 0,0:21:21.42,0:21:22.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,S-Sure.
Comment: 0,0:21:23.92,0:21:27.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}I'm Junta Azumaya,\Nand I'll be playing the main character.
Comment: 0,0:21:25.01,0:21:27.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even now, I feel like\NI'm going to pounce on you.{\i0}
Comment: 0,0:21:29.05,0:21:31.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm sorry, Takato.{\i0}
Comment: 0,0:21:31.10,0:21:33.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}I'll do my very best\Nand I look forward to working with you!
Comment: 0,0:21:32.18,0:21:33.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}But I swear...{\i0}
Comment: 0,0:21:34.52,0:21:36.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm going to make you mine.{\i0}
Comment: 0,0:21:37.61,0:21:40.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}So we start shooting next week.
Comment: 0,0:21:40.32,0:21:42.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}I look forward to working with all of you.
Comment: 0,0:21:42.48,0:21:44.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}I look forward to working with you!
Comment: 0,0:21:48.66,0:21:50.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}All right, let's go.{\i0}
Comment: 0,0:21:53.20,0:21:54.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Mr. Saijo!
Comment: 0,0:23:25.84,0:23:29.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Ever since the day I said "I like you,"
Comment: 0,0:23:29.01,0:23:34.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I've been more self-conscious than ever\Nwhen we do couple-like things.
Comment: 0,0:23:34.76,0:23:36.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,It's kind of a problem.
Comment: 0,0:23:36.43,0:23:39.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,hug8\N"H-Hands off my swim trunks."
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.79,0:00:27.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Každý den, obloha neustále pluje,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.71,0:00:30.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}jako kdyby někdo opakovaně mačkal tlačítko "hrát".{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.01,0:00:33.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Nikdy se neměnící scéna.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.18,0:00:35.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Žádné nespokojenosti.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.89,0:00:38.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}To musí být důkaz míru.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.93,0:00:43.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Byl jsem odchycen na ulici a vstoupil do šoubyznysu, \Nale svět se okolo mě nijak nezměnil.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.56,0:00:49.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Dnes začíná natáčení drama, které bude značit můj debut jako herce.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.77,0:00:52.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Jako vždycky, \Nvšechno šlo poměrně hladce.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.86,0:00:56.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Jsem Taguchi, manažer Junty Azumaye.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.78,0:00:59.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Azumayo, tohle je režisér, pan Kadokura.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.66,0:01:01.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Junta Azumaya.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.91,0:01:03.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Těší mě.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.87,0:01:05.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,T-Těší mě!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.58,0:01:06.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Chytil se!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.58,0:01:08.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,T-Ty jsi teď hrozně populární, co?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.83,0:01:11.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Barva tvých vlasů a očí je světlá. \NMožná, že jsi Japonec jen napůl?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.38,0:01:13.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Můj děda je Španěl...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.38,0:01:14.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}Saijo-san! Dobré ráno!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.55,0:01:16.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Dobré ráno!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.22,0:01:17.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Dobré ráno.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.76,0:01:19.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Tady je Takato!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.09,0:01:20.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Ahoj, Saijo!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.68,0:01:21.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Dlouho jsme se neviděli.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.14,0:01:27.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Takže tenhle člověk je...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.90,0:01:30.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Takato Saijo.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.28,0:03:08.75,Title,NTP,0,0,0,,objetí 7 "Mohu tě stále mít rád?"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.33,0:03:09.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}Je potěšené Vás potkat. \NJsem Junta Azumaya od Mitsuya Production.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.46,0:03:10.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}Těším se na to s Vámi pracovat.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.54,0:03:19.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Och. Jsem rád, že mám šanci s tebou pracovat na tvém drama debutu.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.97,0:03:21.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Udělejme z toho hit.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.68,0:03:22.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Ano!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.97,0:03:26.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Posuzoval mě?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.47,0:03:31.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}"Lahvička slunce" byla nevinný milostný příběh o mladém parfémurovi(?nwm twl na zabití) s oční nemoci{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.77,0:03:35.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}a holce, která usiluje o to být řemeslnicí skla.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.02,0:03:40.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Má role byla začínajícího hrnčíře a dlouhého přítele hlavní hrdinky, který do ní byl zamilovaný.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.45,0:03:43.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Střih! Dobře, máme to!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.53,0:03:45.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Takže další je scéna mezi Hinatou a Satomi.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.99,0:03:46.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Dobře!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.58,0:03:49.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Azumayo, je tohle opravdu poprvé?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.79,0:03:51.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,To bylo skvělé!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.33,0:03:52.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Děkuji.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.42,0:03:55.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Takže hádám, že jak jsem to udělal bylo dobré.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.75,0:03:59.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Pro teď, vypadá to, že dělat to, co obvykle postačí.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.51,0:04:08.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Uhm...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.64,0:04:11.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}co je tohle?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.27,0:04:13.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Hej, hej, hej, hej!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.14,0:04:15.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Stop! Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.94,0:04:18.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Co je s tím vystoupením té holky?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.86,0:04:19.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}Ugh, tamhle je. Sakamaki, producent!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.36,0:04:24.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Jsem si jistý, že tohle je těžká práce pro modelku nahotinek, ale musíš se alespoň snažit!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.82,0:04:22.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}Nepřibližuj se k němu moc, jinak mu budeš chtít dát nakládačku.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.11,0:04:27.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}Páni, vypadá jako růžové rybí vločky (Sakura Denbu).{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.70,0:04:29.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,P-Pane Sakamaki! Její výstup nebyl tak špatný.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.08,0:04:31.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Dobrá, fajn, zdá se, že tě budu muset poučit
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.41,0:04:33.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,o tom kreativním myšlení, \Nkteré je pro drama potřebné.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.87,0:04:36.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Potom tě vezmu na skleničku, dobře?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.50,0:04:38.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,První obtěžování na pracovišti, \Npak sexuální obtěžování.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.00,0:04:43.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}Zajímalo by mě, pokud ji tady teď zachráním, jestli to bude mít vliv na moji příští práci.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.09,0:04:42.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Děkuji.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.92,0:04:46.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Máš zítra volno? Máš, že?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.38,0:04:46.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}Och, to je jedno.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.68,0:04:48.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}Hej, Azumayo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.68,0:04:49.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Jo. Co bychom tedy měli udělat?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.05,0:04:50.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Asi jít do Ginzy? Dát se nějaké to suši...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.85,0:04:56.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Pardon.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.31,0:05:00.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Pokud tady nebudeme pokračovat, můžeme se posunout na moji další scénu?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.82,0:05:03.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Jen plýtváme časem.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.07,0:05:07.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Tohle má takovou jemnou formu.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.36,0:05:11.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Nemá to tu tuhost skla a jak to držím, cítím jak to je teplé.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.50,0:05:15.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Co?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.92,0:05:16.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Věděl jsem to.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.04,0:05:18.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Jsi přesně jako tahle lahvička.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.04,0:05:21.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Vůně teplého slunce.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.84,0:05:23.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Vyrobila jsi ji?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.51,0:05:27.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Podává takový elegantní výkon.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.30,0:05:29.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Je to jako kdyby každý okamžik byl promyšlený.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.97,0:05:31.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Mé oči ho chtějí sledovat až k jeho konečkům prstů.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.77,0:05:35.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Mám rád tenhle čistý pocit napětí.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.89,0:05:39.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Je to jako kdyby na celý tenhle set přinášel nádech důstojnosti.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.94,0:05:41.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Střih! Dobře, hotovo!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.19,0:05:44.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,No, já teď půjdu.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.61,0:05:46.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,D-Dobrá práce!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.74,0:05:48.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,T-To je můj Saijo!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.82,0:05:51.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Jsi v naprosto jiné lize než tihle nováčci! Dobré, dobré!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.66,0:05:52.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Ty tam.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.91,0:05:54.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Stojíš mi v cestě.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.41,0:05:57.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,P-Promiň.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.71,0:05:58.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Děkuji.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.29,0:06:05.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}Saijo byl ve špatné náladě, protože jste dělali hroznou práci!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.76,0:06:07.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}Měli byste se mu později omluvit!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.38,0:06:10.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Je skoro působivé jak podřadný je.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.80,0:06:12.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Růžové rybí vločky se odhlásili?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.26,0:06:17.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Uhm, omlouvám se, že jsem pana Saijo rozzlobila.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.43,0:06:23.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Och, kdepak, myslím si, že Saijo jen dobře předstíral, aby přesměroval pana Sakamakiho.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.94,0:06:27.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}Tím, že to udělal, pan Sakamaki se musel začít obávat o Saijovu náladu
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.65,0:06:30.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}a nemohl si z nikým z nás nic začít.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.16,0:06:32.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}Upřímně, to měla být moje práce.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.99,0:06:33.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}Jsem ubohý.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.83,0:06:37.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Takato, musíš být tak skvělý.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.21,0:06:43.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Takže takové to je být na setu drama.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.50,0:06:47.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Nemyslím si, že by to bylo něco, co by jsem kdy zažil. Především...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.59,0:06:49.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Chtěl bych objednat občerstvení pro štáb,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.80,0:06:52.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,a prosím přidejte sortiment sladkostí, které by dívky měly rády.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.55,0:06:56.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Ano, jen chci trochu zlepšit morálku na setu.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.22,0:06:59.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Saijo-san nešel domů?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.02,0:07:03.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Jsem v pořádku. Kolik let si myslíš, že to už dělám?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.61,0:07:09.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}Silní lidé jako on jsou prostě ideální jen tím, že udělají něco jako je tohle.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.19,0:07:07.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Ano, omlouvám se za nepříjemnosti, Sasaki-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.53,0:07:09.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Prosím, objednej to. Děkuji.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.36,0:07:17.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Příště, co si ten producent vztyčí hlavu a ukáže se na setu,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.37,0:07:21.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,ztrapním ho tak hrozně, že už si nikdy na sebe růžovou nevezme.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.75,0:07:26.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Jaké "kreativní myšlení"?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.84,0:07:29.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Měl by se první předělat od toho než se narodil!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.63,0:07:33.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Aha. Tohle je jaký opravdu je.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.80,0:07:36.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Jeho obličej, když není na setu...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.76,0:07:40.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Myslím tím, je to vážně jiné, \Nale člověče, je to srandovní!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.14,0:07:40.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}Potřebuju více cukru! No tak, serotonine! Dej mi trochu více!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.77,0:07:46.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,No, to stačí o té malé rybce, ale tenhle Junta Azumaya...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.36,0:07:51.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Bylo to už nějakou tu dobu, co jsem se musel potýkat s větší otravou.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.86,0:07:53.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Aha.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.20,0:07:58.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Neustále se na mě díval s odporem.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.50,0:08:02.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hádám, že tohle je jaké to být nenáviděn.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.63,0:08:05.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Saijo-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.21,0:08:07.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Dobrá práce.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.88,0:08:09.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,A-Azumayo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.05,0:08:10.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Máte rád horkou čokoládu?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.59,0:08:15.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Jak dlouho jsi tu byl, Azumayo?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.64,0:08:16.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Ne dlouho.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.47,0:08:17.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Och, aha.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.64,0:08:19.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Tím "ne dlouho" myslíš 4-5 minut?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.47,0:08:21.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Ne, okolo 30 sekund.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.48,0:08:22.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Och, vážně?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.98,0:08:26.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Saijo-san, děkuji za to předtím.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.07,0:08:30.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Och, věděl jsi, co jsem dělal, co?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.48,0:08:32.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Kadokura-san to vysvětlil.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.86,0:08:33.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Och.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.03,0:08:35.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Dlužím mu.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.70,0:08:41.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Jeho řasy jsou tak dlouhé, že vrhají stín.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.16,0:08:39.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}Tak to nemusím vysvětlovat.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.45,0:08:45.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,No, pokud se tam věci uklidnily, vrátím se do studia.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.71,0:08:47.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Musím Kadokurovi-san poděkovat.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.92,0:08:49.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Uhm, Saijo-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.21,0:08:55.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Opravdu jsem vděčný, že mám tuhle šanci s Vámi pracovat.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.51,0:08:57.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Těším se na to s Vámi pracovat, dokud to nebude u konce.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.05,0:09:00.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Jsi vděčný?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.06,0:09:03.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Tak bych taky měl do toho dát vše.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.81,0:09:07.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Takže se tak budeš cítit až do úplného konce.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.11,0:09:15.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Pracujme spolu dobře, Azumayo.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.37,0:09:20.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Cože?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.58,0:09:23.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Co je tohle?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.12,0:09:25.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Moje hruď.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.42,0:09:33.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}Poprvé, slyšel jsem zvuk hlasité oblohy.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.77,0:09:49.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Pomalu své oči otevře jako kdyby vydechoval, a pak se na mě podívá.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.73,0:09:56.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Jeho výrazy, a způsob, jakým hýbe jeho pohledem. \NUspokojuje to všechny diváky s jeho výkonem.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.82,0:09:58.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Dává nám, co chceme.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.16,0:10:00.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Co chceme?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.20,0:10:02.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Co chci?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.29,0:10:05.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Odkud to pochází?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.04,0:10:08.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Tohle víření v mém žaludku...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.71,0:10:12.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Co to sakra je?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.59,0:10:16.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Mám ho ráda. Proto jsem s ním.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.34,0:10:20.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Časem nebude moct vidět ani tebe, ani tvou práci.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.47,0:10:21.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I pokud nebude vidět...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.80,0:10:25.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I pokud nebude moct vidět, bude vědět dotykem.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.18,0:10:26.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Vytuší mě vůní.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.31,0:10:29.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Hinato, vyber si mě.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.40,0:10:31.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Kosuke, přestaňme o tomhle mluvit.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.81,0:10:36.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Buď mou. Vždy se na tebe budu dívat, stejně jako doteď.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.69,0:10:38.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Počkej, Kosuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.49,0:10:41.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Střih! Azumayo, Natsume, dobrá práce!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.24,0:10:43.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Dobrá práce!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.28,0:10:44.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Dobrá práce.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.92,0:10:55.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Omluvte mě.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.34,0:11:01.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Dobrá práce.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.18,0:11:02.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Jo, dobrá práce.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.97,0:11:07.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Co bych měl udělat? Jsme tu jen my dva, \Nale bylo by nevhodné, kdybych si od něj sedl daleko.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.39,0:11:09.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Můžu se sednout vedle Vás?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.85,0:11:12.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Zajisté.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.90,0:11:15.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Totálně mě tam nechce.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.82,0:11:24.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Tohle je nepříjemné, ale možná se ho zeptám na to předtím.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.70,0:11:27.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Pokud je něco, co jsem udělal a urazilo ho to, omluvím se.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.91,0:11:29.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Uhm, Saijo-san, já—
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.75,0:11:30.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Mám ho ráda.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.08,0:11:35.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Mám ho ráda. Proto jsem s ním.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.59,0:11:37.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- Uhm, Saijo-san? \N- Další věta.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.42,0:11:39.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Z té poslední scény.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.38,0:11:45.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Časem nebude moct vidět ani tebe, ani tvou práci.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.60,0:11:47.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I pokud neuvidí...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.01,0:11:50.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I pokud nebude moct vidět, bude vědět dotykem.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.35,0:11:52.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- Vytuší mě podle— \N- Vyber si mě.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.23,0:11:54.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Kosuke, přestaňme o tomhle mluv—
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.02,0:11:56.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Buď mou. Já...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.82,0:11:58.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Drž ji něžně v mém náručí...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.61,0:12:01.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ne, drž ji jako kdybych ji kradl.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.90,0:12:06.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Vždy se na tebe budu dívat, tak jako doteď.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.03,0:12:08.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Budu následovat mé pocity.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.79,0:12:10.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Azumayo.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.45,0:12:12.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,To bylo mnohem lepší.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.83,0:12:15.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Mnohem lepší než jen odříkávání textu.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.50,0:12:19.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Namísto myšlení logicky, sedí ti víc, když hraješ podle svých emocí.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.17,0:12:22.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Možná by ses o sobě měl více dozvědět.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.80,0:12:24.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,O sobě?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.55,0:12:27.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Přísahám, že sedíš na zlatém dolu.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.89,0:12:31.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Uhm, Saijo-san. Zajímalo by mě, co vlastně chci.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.23,0:12:33.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Nic!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.69,0:12:35.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Děkuji.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.81,0:12:39.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,No tak já si zdřímnu, dokud nedorazíme do cíle.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.07,0:12:41.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Jistě! Dobrou noc.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.74,0:12:48.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Já, o kterém jsem neměl potuchy je pomalu vytažený na povrch.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.49,0:12:53.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Co to s ním je?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.42,0:12:57.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,A akce!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.88,0:13:01.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Nevadí ti poflakovat se kolem v noci?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.05,0:13:04.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Ty jsi...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.13,0:13:06.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Nepamatuješ si mě?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.72,0:13:11.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Nebo možná teď z takové dálky obličeje už nevidíš?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.89,0:13:15.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Jsi Kosuke, že? Poznávám tvůj hlas.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.06,0:13:16.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Nechápeš to, že jo?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.15,0:13:18.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Ale chápu.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.27,0:13:20.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Vím, že si ji vážíš.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.11,0:13:22.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Vím, co mi chceš říct.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.28,0:13:24.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Rozumím ti dokonale.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.78,0:13:26.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Amamiyo-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.95,0:13:30.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Repliky, emoce, ze mě vycházejí přirozeně.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.83,0:13:34.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Chci všechno, co mám na něj hodit. Víc, víc.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.41,0:13:37.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Amamiyo-san, vůči ni, jak se k—
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.67,0:13:47.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}Říkal jsem ti, ať to zkontroluješ!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.22,0:13:49.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}- O-Omlouvám se! Ručníky! Ručníky! \N- Jste v pořádku, Saijo-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.60,0:13:55.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Slyšel jsem něco.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.65,0:13:59.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}Azumayo.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.69,0:14:03.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}V mé mysli, obloha bouří.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.52,0:14:03.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}Proč jsi...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.57,0:14:07.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Proč se tak krčíš?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.91,0:14:11.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Proč se na mě tak díváš?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.57,0:14:11.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}Co?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.54,0:14:16.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Je to proto, že mě nenávidíš?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.04,0:14:16.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}Azu... mayo...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.96,0:14:23.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Saijo! Azumayo!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.92,0:14:24.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Jste v pořádku?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.21,0:14:26.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Ano.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.13,0:14:30.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Nejsem tak zmoklý, takže se postarejte o Azumayu.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.59,0:14:31.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,D-Dobře!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.10,0:14:34.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Promiň. Ale díky.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.89,0:14:35.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Není za co.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.89,0:14:39.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Co jsem to dělal?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.31,0:14:42.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Dobře.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.90,0:14:45.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Dal bych ti úplně všechno.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.82,0:14:50.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kdyby jsme nebyli přerušení, políbil bych ho.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.41,0:14:52.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Políbil?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.45,0:14:55.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ne. Nebylo by to nic tak něžného.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.12,0:14:57.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Nikdy jsem se tak necítil.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.33,0:15:00.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Bylo to jako bych se stal zvířetem.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.42,0:15:05.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Jen na okamžik, vypadal vystrašeně.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.42,0:15:08.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Možná mě zase nenávidí?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.60,0:15:17.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Tohle musí být to, co viděl.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.68,0:15:20.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Obličej muže, který podlehl touze.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.10,0:15:23.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Miluji tě.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.15,0:15:24.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,P-Počkej, Kosuke.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.48,0:15:25.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Nemůžu čekat.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.65,0:15:27.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Čekal jsem už dost.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.86,0:15:30.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Hinato.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.41,0:15:32.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,To bylo skvělé!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.78,0:15:35.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Tohle byla ta nejlepší scéna, kterou jste spolu měli.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.28,0:15:38.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Azumayo, co to sakra? \NNáhle probuzení!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.58,0:15:39.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Probuzení?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.66,0:15:41.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Změnil jsi se od té poslední lokace.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.92,0:15:43.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Způsobilo to něco?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.42,0:15:51.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Ano, něco tam bylo.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.68,0:15:59.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Cože?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.10,0:16:03.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Saijo-san, necítíte se dobře?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.86,0:16:06.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Vypadáte trošku bledě.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.86,0:16:09.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Ne, jsem v pořádku.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.28,0:16:12.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Jsem rád, že máš dost sebevědomí se starat o můj blahobyt.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.66,0:16:15.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Ale ujisti se, že zůstaneš soustředěný.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.66,0:16:17.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Ano.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.74,0:16:21.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Ale, um, myslím, že máte menší horečku.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.01,0:16:31.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Promiň.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.05,0:16:33.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Ne, je to moje chyba. Omlouvám se.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.22,0:16:40.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Bolí to. Bolí to, ale...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.18,0:16:45.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}ten moment kontaktu, i s tím okamžikem bolesti, táhne to až do konce.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.86,0:16:51.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Pardon. Nastupuji.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.58,0:16:59.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,A předtím...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.91,0:17:02.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- Ano? \N- Poranil jsem ti ruku?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.33,0:17:05.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Ne, nic to nebylo.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.58,0:17:07.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Och. Dobré.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.34,0:17:12.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Když jeden herec zraní druhého, není to nic k smíchu.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.13,0:17:16.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Chci ho obejmout a zvednout.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.59,0:17:17.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ale...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.55,0:17:22.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ale jsem si jistý, že se jen chce co nejrychleji dostat pryč ode mně a z tohohle uzavřeného prostoru.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.15,0:17:28.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Je opravdu v pořádku?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.77,0:17:31.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Vypadá, že chodí normálně, ale...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.57,0:17:36.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Strachovat se o něj příliš ho jen dostane do horší nálady.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.28,0:17:40.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Saijo-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.12,0:17:43.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Omluvte mě.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.54,0:17:47.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Jste mnohem teplejší, než jsem si myslel. Nemocnice...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.79,0:17:50.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Sakra. Mám jen svou motorku.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.71,0:17:53.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Promiňte. Potřebuju taxi.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.59,0:17:56.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Lokace je studio v Aoumi. Ano, správně.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.30,0:17:59.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Ano. Děkuji.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.64,0:18:05.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Vím, že nechceš, abych se tě dotýkal, ale pro teď to vydrž.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.44,0:18:17.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Takže touha někoho si vážit je spojená s touhou někoho chtít jen pro sebe.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.53,0:18:19.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Saijo-san.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.57,0:18:22.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Zamiloval jsem se do tebe.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.70,0:18:26.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Promiň. I pokud mě nenávidíš...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.96,0:18:30.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Mohu tě neustále mít rád?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.80,0:18:39.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Och, tamhle je. \NTady Sasaki. Jdu dovnitř!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.80,0:18:40.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Dobrý večer!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.93,0:18:42.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Dobrý večer.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.05,0:18:43.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Omlouvám se, že jste se musel obtěžovat.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.89,0:18:45.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Kdepak, vůbec nic takového.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.56,0:18:48.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Doktor říkal, že s IV a dostatkem spánku by měl by v pořádku.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.60,0:18:53.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Zajímalo mě, o čem to bylo, když jste zavolal mou agenturu.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.11,0:18:55.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Muselo být těžké ho sem dostat, nést takového vysokého muže.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.24,0:18:58.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Kdepak, byl lehký.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.61,0:19:01.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Byl jsem trochu překvapený, jak štíhlý je.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.95,0:19:04.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Och, neříkej mu to, dobře?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.33,0:19:07.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Je to jeho komplex, jak těžké pro něj je získat svaly.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.00,0:19:12.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Můžeš jít, Azumayo.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.25,0:19:14.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Děkuji za dnešek.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.55,0:19:17.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Když se Takato probudí, řeknu mu vše, co jsi udělal.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.59,0:19:21.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Pokud možno, neříkejte mu, že jsem ho se přinesl.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.05,0:19:24.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Stydíš se za to?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.97,0:19:25.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Ano.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.27,0:19:30.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}Vypadá to, že jsem neudělal nic jiného než Saija-san v tomto natáčení jen otravoval.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.02,0:19:34.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}Nenech, aby tě to dostalo. On je ten, co je neustále rozmrzelý.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.73,0:19:35.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}Ale no tak.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.19,0:19:39.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Je neobvyklé, aby s někým otevřeně jednal jako s nepřítelem.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.36,0:19:43.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Možná to znamená, že pro tebe má obrovské očekávání.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.55,0:20:02.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Tahle bolest, zármutek, sladkost, a příval...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.14,0:20:06.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Nejspíš je nemůžu nechat zmizet.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.27,0:20:10.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Motorka je na nic.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.77,0:20:12.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Potřebuju auto.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.69,0:20:16.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Abych mohl toho, kdo je mi nejcennějším, zavést kamkoli by potřeboval.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.19,0:20:21.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Tohle natáčení je skoro u konce.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.57,0:20:27.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Dobrá, zůstaň takhle, dokud tě nezavolají.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.70,0:20:29.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Rozumím.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.46,0:20:35.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Tohle je poslední den.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.92,0:20:43.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ne. Nenechám to být poslední den.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.39,0:20:49.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Od té doby, co jsem tě potkal, naučil jsem se, co to opravdu znamená něco "chtít".{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.60,0:20:53.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Dostihnu tě, Takato.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.53,0:21:02.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Takže když se potkáme příště, budeme bok po boku{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.74,0:21:07.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}a budu moct tyhle pocity vyjádřit a vzít tě do náručí.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.91,0:21:12.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Upevním své odhodlání a začnu se připravovat, abych mohl získat to, co je mi drahé.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.34,0:21:21.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Nejdříve, mohli bychom mít pár slov od našeho hlavního hrdiny, Azumaye?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.42,0:21:22.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,J-Jistě.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.92,0:21:27.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}Jsme Junta Azumaya, a budu hrát hlavní postavu.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.01,0:21:27.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}I teď, mám pocit, že se na tebe vrhnu.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.05,0:21:31.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Promiň, Takato.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.10,0:21:33.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}Dám do toho úplně vše a těším se, že s vámi mohu pracovat!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.18,0:21:33.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ale přísahám...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.52,0:21:36.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}že tě udělám svým.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.61,0:21:40.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}Takže začneme natáčet příští týden.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.32,0:21:42.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}Těším se s vámi všemi pracovat.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.48,0:21:44.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}Těším se s vámi pracovat!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.66,0:21:50.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Dobrá, pojďme.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.20,0:21:54.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Saijo-san!
